entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Boba Fett directed you to  protect a gungan politician, named Nalske, who had a death mark out on him. You took out the bounty hunter hunting Nalskel. Hopefully , you do not make matters worse by saving this gungan politician.
entries.journal_entry_description: According to Nalskel, an up and coming gungan politician on Naboo, a bounty hunter named Soris has been hired by his opponents to end his political career. Luckily for Nalskel, Soris hasn't . Find him and defeat him.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: You cleaned up Faeto's problem very nicely. Body count wasn't too bad. Now you get to hunt one of our own. Nalskel should contact you soon with the particulars.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Boba Fett told you to expect a communication from Nalskel. It sounds like he's a fellow bounty hunter and that he's going to send some work your way.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Mesa so happy Fetta send yousa to mesa. Moa Bounty Hunter after mesa for mysa veiws polictica. Makea himsa deada. Soris isa hisa namea.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Nalskel has heard of you. Many rumors are flying around that you're a bounty hunter who does a good job and who doesn't ask questions. He wants you to find a bounty hunter named Soris who has been tracking Nalskel for days.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Nalskel's associates have tracked Soris down. Apparently, Soris is on a mission. If he's not at his camp, find a clue that might tell you where he might have gone.
entries.task05_comm_message_text: Datapad say Soris worksa with moua moua Brovos. Go to Brovos campsa and killsa Brovos until theysa say uncla.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Nalskel believes that Soris has teamed up with Borvo the Hutt and his underlings to go after him. He wants you to kill some of Borvo's underlings and teach them a lesson about helping an assassin.
entries.task07_comm_message_text: Soris himsa has nosa friends left. Give Soris death mark and killsa him moua moua dead.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Give Soris his Death Mark before you kill him.
entries.task11_comm_message_text: Hesa moua moua happy. Yousa got mesa Death Mark back! Nowsa mesa political career can take off. Mesa going to the Imperial adminstration.
